    <div class="home-content">
        <h1>ChequeYourSelf</h1>

        <p class="tagline">
            A simple, reliable payroll support system for small businesses.
        </p>

        <div class="homepageDescription">
            <p>
                ChequeYourSelf is a payroll calculation support system for small businesses that need a reliable
                way to track employee hours and configure common payroll deductions. The database supports
                up to 50 businesses with up to 50 employees each (~2,500 employees total) and is designed for
                frequent updates as employees submit time entries and managers update deduction settings.
            </p>

            <p>
                The system allows managers to record and review hours worked by date and assign deduction
                rules to employees (e.g., taxes and benefits). Using time entries, hourly rates, payroll frequency
                presets, and configured deductions, the application can calculate an estimated gross and net
                paycheck for a selected date range.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
